Package: nycsets
Title: NYC Film Permits Data
Version: 0.0.1.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Kieran", "Healy", , "kjhealy@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9114-981X"))
Description: Film, television, and other production permits issued by the
    New York City Mayor's Office of Media and Entertainment (MOME). Includes
    the main permits table and companion long tables linking permits to
    community boards, police precincts, and ZIP codes.
